<isis lang="en">
    <stitle>ANTILOCK BRAKES/ TRACTION CONTROL TROUBLESHOOTING: BENDIX - 9100, 9200, 9300 and 9400 Models Built March 1,
        1998 and After - TROUBLESHOOTING - INITIAL START-UP TEST PROCEDURE
    </stitle>
    <svcsection/>
    <svcproc id="x0404203" svcproctype="test" graphiccount="0">
        <title>INITIAL START-UP TEST PROCEDURE</title>
        <table id="t0404201" tblwidth="full-page" frame="all" numbered="no" view="reveal">
            <title>Initial Start-Up Test Procedure</title>
            <tgroup cols="6" align="center" charoff="50" char="c">
                <colspec colname="1" colwidth="0.55in"/>
                <colspec colname="2" colwidth="0.57in"/>
                <colspec colname="3" colwidth="2.17in"/>
                <colspec colname="4" colwidth="0.75in"/>
                <colspec colname="5" colwidth="0.99in"/>
                <colspec colname="6" colwidth="1.64in"/>
                <spanspec namest="1" nameend="6" spanname="s1t6" align="center"/>
                <thead>
                    <row>
                        <entry colname="1">
                            <para>STEP</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="2">
                            <para>KEY</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="3">
                            <para>ACTION</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="4">
                            <para>SPEC.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="5">
                            <para>YES / IN SPEC.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="6">
                            <para>NO / OUT OF SPEC.</para>
                        </entry>
                    </row>
                </thead>
                <tbody valign="top">
                    <row>
                        <entry colname="1">
                            <para>1.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="2">
                            <para>Off</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="3">
                            <para>Is vehicle equipped with Traction Control?</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="4">
                            <para></para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="5">
                            <para>Go to next step.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="6">
                            <para>Go to Step 5.</para>
                        </entry>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                        <entry colname="1">
                            <para>2.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="2">
                            <para>On</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="3">
                            <para>Place the traction control panel switch to the ON position. Turn key ON and note if
                                the Traction Active light blinked ON, then turned OFF.
                            </para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="4">
                            <para>Light blinked ON then OFF?</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="5">
                            <para>Go to Step 5.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="6">
                            <para>Go to next step.</para>
                        </entry>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                        <entry colname="1">
                            <para>3.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="2">
                            <para>On</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="3">
                            <para>Is the Traction Active light ON?</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="4">
                            <para></para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="5">
                            <para>Go to
                                <hotlnk document="s04042_27.xml" xrefid="t0404221">TESTING TRACTION CONTROL MODULATOR,
                                    PART A.
                                    <xref refid="t0404221"/>
                                </hotlnk>
                            </para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="6">
                            <para>Go to next step.</para>
                        </entry>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                        <entry colname="1">
                            <para>4.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="2">
                            <para>On</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="3">
                            <para>Is ABS dash light ON?</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="4">
                            <para></para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="5">
                            <para>Go to
                                <hotlnk document="s04042_25.xml" xrefid="t0404219">TESTING TRACTION CONTROL ON/ OFF
                                    SWITCH
                                    <xref refid="t0404219"/>
                                </hotlnk>
                                .
                            </para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="6">
                            <para>Go to
                                <hotlnk document="s04042_8.xml" xrefid="t0404202">ABS WARNING LIGHT DOES NOT TURN ON
                                    <xref refid="t0404202"/>
                                </hotlnk>
                                .
                            </para>
                        </entry>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                        <entry colname="1">
                            <para>5.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="2">
                            <para>On</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="3">
                            <para>Is ABS dash light ON?</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="4">
                            <para></para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="5">
                            <para>Go to next step.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="6">
                            <para>Go to
                                <hotlnk document="s04042_8.xml" xrefid="t0404202">ABS WARNING LIGHT DOES NOT TURN ON
                                    <xref refid="t0404202"/>
                                </hotlnk>
                                .
                            </para>
                        </entry>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                        <entry colname="1">
                            <para>6.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="2">
                            <para>On</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="3">
                            <para>Note if the ABS light blinked when it turned ON.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="4">
                            <para>Light blinked.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="5">
                            <para>Go to next step.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="6">
                            <para>Go to
                                <hotlnk document="s04042_9.xml" xrefid="t0404203">INSPECTING FOR ILLUMINATED LEDS, PART
                                    A
                                    <xref refid="t0404203"/>
                                </hotlnk>
                                .
                            </para>
                        </entry>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                        <entry colname="1">
                            <para>7.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="2">
                            <para>On</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="3">
                            <para>ABS warning light flashes, then turns ON. Drive vehicle above 7 MPH for at least 5
                                seconds and note if ABS warning light stays ON.
                            </para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="4">
                            <para>ABS light ON.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="5">
                            <para>Go to
                                <hotlnk document="s04042_9.xml" xrefid="t0404203">INSPECTION FOR ILLUMINATED LEDS, PART
                                    A
                                    <xref refid="t0404203"/>
                                </hotlnk>
                                .
                            </para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="6">
                            <para>The ABS system is functioning properly.</para>
                        </entry>
                    </row>
                </tbody>
            </tgroup>
        </table>
    </svcproc>
